sfxSettingKey.description: Leave this empty if there is only one setting for all sounds

motionThreshold.title: Motion Threshold
motionThreshold.description: Number of meters moved in one frame before CCD is enabled

sweptSphereRadius.title: Swept Sphere Radius
sweptSphereRadius.description: This should be below the half extent of the collision volume. E.g For an object of dimensions 1 meter, try 0.2

zCurve.title: Z distance Curve
zCurve.description: The x-axis represents the ratio of the resolution divided by 2.

templateName.title: Template Name
templateName.description: This value is used for saving in the localStorage. Make sure to make it unique, so it doesn't override any other storages.

hasRewardedAd.title: Has Rewarded Ad
hasRewardedAd.description: You can change this value for testing purposes. This will not affect the real famobi API
